## Progress Report Format

APPEND to tasks/progress.txt (never replace, always append):

## [Date/Time] - [Story ID]: [Story Title]
- What was implemented
- Files changed
- TDD observations:
  - Tests written before code: [yes/no, which tests]
  - RED-GREEN-REFACTOR cycles completed: [count]
- Review findings:
  - Spec compliance: [pass/issues found]
  - Code quality: [pass/issues found]
- Verification evidence:
  - Test output: [summary]
  - Typecheck output: [summary]
- **Learnings for future iterations:**
  - Patterns discovered
  - Gotchas encountered
  - Useful context
